---
import GamesLayout from '../../layouts/GamesLayout.astro';
---

<GamesLayout title="Vestige" description="Vestige — a narrative metroidvania by Quiet Atlas. Explore the architecture of a damaged mind. Confront grief, identity, and what the mind tried to bury.">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="game-hero">
    <div class="game-hero-visual game-hero-image vestige-hero-bg">
      <div class="game-hero-overlay"></div>
      <div class="game-hero-content container fade-in">
        <span class="game-hero-label">Narrative Metroidvania · Psychological · Atmospheric</span>
        <h1 class="game-hero-title">Vestige</h1>
        <p class="game-hero-tagline">Explore the architecture of a damaged mind.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About -->
  <section class="game-about container">
    <div class="content-width">
      <div class="game-lead fade-in">
        <p class="lead-text">
          After a catastrophic personal history and the loss of his children, neuroscientist
          <strong>Elias Noe</strong> uses experimental technology to erase his memories. The player
          inhabits his fractured consciousness while his body lies in a coma. You explore the
          architecture of a damaged mind — not as a tourist, but as the one who must face what
          was buried.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="pull-quote fade-in">
        "Vestige is not about defeating enemies. It is about confronting grief, navigating fractured identity, and rebuilding meaning from fragments."
      </div>

      <div class="game-details fade-in">
        <h2>Emotional Experience</h2>
        <p>
          Vestige is about confronting grief, navigating fractured identity, rebuilding meaning
          from fragments, and facing what the mind tried to bury. Progression is emotional
          integration — a metroidvania where the real unlock is acceptance.
        </p>

        <h2>World Design</h2>
        <p>
          The world represents neurological and emotional states: decaying memory corridors,
          collapsing cognitive structures, authoritarian memory fragments, neural pathways as
          traversal routes, and subconscious defensive entities. The environment tells the story.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="game-features stagger-children">
        <div class="feature-card card">
          <h3>Memory Fragmentation</h3>
          <p>Abilities unlock access to previously unreachable mental regions. Progress through the mind, not just the map.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card card">
          <h3>Rewind — Regret Essence</h3>
          <p>Rewind to a past state: first position, then health, then debuffs, then offensive effects and singularity pulls. Revisiting trauma, in mechanic form.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card card">
          <h3>Weapon System — Stages of Grief</h3>
          <p>Each weapon embodies a psychological state: denial, anger, bargaining, depression, acceptance. You learn emotional mastery through combat.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="signature fade-in">
        <p><strong>Signature identity:</strong> A metroidvania where progression is emotional integration.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Info Sidebar -->
  <section class="game-info container">
    <div class="info-grid fade-in">
      <div class="info-block">
        <h3>Status</h3>
        <p>In Development</p>
      </div>
      <div class="info-block">
        <h3>Genre</h3>
        <p>Narrative Metroidvania</p>
      </div>
      <div class="info-block">
        <h3>Platform</h3>
        <p>PC / Mac</p>
      </div>
      <div class="info-block">
        <h3>Engine</h3>
        <p>Godot</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta container">
    <div class="cta-inner fade-in">
      <hr class="ornamental" />
      <p class="cta-text">Vestige is still being drawn. Follow us to walk with it when it's ready.</p>
      <a href="https://quietatlas.itch.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-large">Follow on itch.io</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</GamesLayout>

<style>
  /* ─── Game Hero ─── */
  .game-hero {
    margin-top: calc(-1 * var(--nav-height));
  }

  .game-hero-visual {
    min-height: 60vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    position: relative;
    padding: var(--space-2xl) 0 var(--space-xl);
  }

  .game-hero-image {
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
  }

  .vestige-hero-bg {
    background-image: url('/images/games/vestige-concept.png');
    background-color: #0a0a1a;
  }

  .game-hero-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(8, 8, 12, 0.3) 0%, rgba(8, 8, 12, 0.9) 100%);
  }

  .game-hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .game-hero-label {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .game-hero-title {
    font-size: clamp(3.5rem, 10vw, 7rem);
    line-height: 0.95;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .game-hero-tagline {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.5vw, 1.35rem);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* ─── Game About ─── */
  .game-about {
    padding: var(--space-2xl) 0;
  }

  .lead-text {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .game-details {
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .game-details h2 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .game-details p {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .signature {
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
    padding: var(--space-md);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);
    background: var(--bg-alt);
    border-radius: 0 var(--radius-sm) var(--radius-sm) 0;
  }

  .signature p {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* ─── Features ─── */
  .game-features {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-md);
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .feature-card h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .feature-card p {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .game-features {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  /* ─── Info Grid ─── */
  .game-info {
    padding: var(--space-xl) 0;
  }

  .info-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-md);
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    background: var(--bg-alt);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  }

  .info-block h3 {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .info-block p {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text);
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .info-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  /* ─── CTA ─── */
  .cta {
    padding: var(--space-xl) 0 var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .cta-inner {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta-text {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }
</style>
